---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Reformer 1:1 | HALM Wellness">
  <div class="container mx-auto py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Reformer 1:1</h1>
    <p class="mb-6">Experience personalized reformer pilates with dedicated instructor attention.</p>
    
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>Our private reformer sessions offer the ultimate personalized Pilates experience. Working one-on-one with an expert instructor allows for a completely customized approach that addresses your specific goals, challenges, and needs.</p>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Benefits of Private Sessions</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Personalized programming tailored to your unique needs</li>
        <li>Focused attention on proper form and technique</li>
        <li>Adaptations for injuries or special considerations</li>
        <li>Flexible scheduling to fit your lifestyle</li>
        <li>Faster progress toward your specific goals</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2 class="mt-8">Our Instructors</h2>
      <p>Our certified Pilates instructors bring years of experience and specialized training to help you achieve optimal results safely and effectively.</p>
      
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-primary-dark transition">Book a Session</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
